deseq2plot              Make a plot from deseq results
gm_mean                 Calculate the geometric mean
make.richness.map       Make a map of diversity scores for plotting
make_deseq              Make a DESeq S4 object using a user design and
                        a phyloseq S4 object
make_phyloseq           Make phyloseq S4 object
otu2melt                A function to melt data from an S4 phyloseq
                        table with metadata
phylodeseqr-package     What the package does (short line) ~~ package
                        title ~~
pick_directory          A function to choose the working director
result2taxa             Add taxa from a phyloseq object to the results
                        analysis of a DESeq object
richness_plot           Plot diversity data from the make_richness
                        function
